<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>450</hymn_number>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Facang le mitsur he a khat, Keimah roconak khua ka phak, Khi khuachung
 cu zungzal a ceu, Zan muihnak zong a um ti lo.

[C1]
   Maw Beaulah ram, Maw ram sung bik, Tlangcung par in ka dir tikah Kei
   ca a remh inn tha ka hmuh, Rili khatte-lei kam ah khin, Ceunak ram kha
   keimah ka hmuh, Kei ca zungzal umnak a si.

[V2]
 Khamhbawi nih keimah he aa chok, Dawtnak in kannih kan i chawn A kut
 in lam a ka hruai i, Vancung hawi-komhnak tha a si.

[C2]
   Maw Beaulah ram, Maw ram sung bik, Tlangcung par in ka dir tikah Kei
   ca a remh inn tha ka hmuh, Rili khatte-lei kam ah khin, Ceunak ram kha
   keimah ka hmuh, Kei ca zungzal umnak a si.

[V3]
 Zungzal a hring thing umnak in, Rim hmuinak kha thli nih a hranh, Uai
 lo pangpar zungzal a kho, Nunnak cerhti zungzal a luang.

[C3]
   Maw Beaulah ram, Maw ram sung bik, Tlangcung par in ka dir tikah Kei
   ca a remh inn tha ka hmuh, Rili khatte-lei kam ah khin, Ceunak ram kha
   keimah ka hmuh, Kei ca zungzal umnak a si.</lyrics>
<title>BEAULAH RAM CH450</title>
</song>